The TUMBLE FEATURE means that after every spin, winning combinations are paid and all winning symbols disappear. During the free spins round WILD symbols hit with a random multiplier of 2x, 3x or 5x. Every time a WILD is involved in a winning combination it's multiplier is accumulated in a tumble multiplier indicator. All WILD multipliers that hit during a tumble sequence multiply between each other. At the end of the tumble sequence the accumulated multiplier applies to the total win of that tumble sequence.
WILD symbol appears only on reels 2, 3, 4 and 5.
When buying the FREE SPINS feature 4, 5 or 6 BONUS symbols hit randomly awarding 12, 17 or 22 free spins respectively.
Bet multiplier 25x - The chance to win FREE SPINS naturally is doubled, more BONUS symbols are present on the reels but symbol paytable is not affected and they pay as for 20x bet multiplier.
